Bộ phim là lựa chọn hấp dẫn cho những ai yêu thích thể loại kinh dị tâm lý, văn hóa thập niên 80 và câu chuyện về tuổi trẻ nổi loạn.</p>","tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"224361","season":1,"vote_average":6.9,"vote_count":59},"modified":"2025-06-01T15:27:10.000Z","cast":["Julie Bowen","Anna Camp","Emjay Anthony","Chiara Aurelia","Kezii Curtis","Nikki Hahn","Bruce Campbell","Garret Dillahunt","Jessica Treska","Milly Shapiro","Nolan North","Allison Scagliotti"],"director":[],"cast_meta":[{"name":"Julie Bowen","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Julie Bowen","tmdb_id":31171,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/5ewqnbPAY0EzZObGHIKU4VsCanD.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/31171"},{"name":"Anna Camp","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Anna Camp","tmdb_id":221098,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/32H0SJbTK3tvLVgf3X1aiaUdcxe.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/221098"},{"name":"Emjay Anthony","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Emjay Anthony","tmdb_id":1259762,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/u7R4CWfmTqsLexejsMNxWrPYKMG.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1259762"},{"name":"Chiara Aurelia","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Chiara Aurelia","tmdb_id":1590225,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/p0pKPznL6pJ2PlKIarLMrXjCvNF.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1590225"},{"name":"Kezii Curtis","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Kezii Curtis","tmdb_id":2446198,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/fxHSbWmnQblXk9VfPBYsSqFThue.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2446198"},{"name":"Nikki Hahn","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Nikki Hahn","tmdb_id":966902,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/loiqZVESxkm0YDcEVulrdhcTnQc.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/966902"},{"name":"Bruce Campbell","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Bruce Campbell","tmdb_id":11357,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/p9335ljr7luOWsfwZSOlsIzFJKE.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/11357